{"id":232969861,"title":"斜背包推薦","content":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/0e000097-68dd-44df-a7fa-f4e3c76141b7/full.jpeg\n事情是這樣的\n之前集資買了個h牌的手機包\n用了一段時間\n覺得不錯用\n如果出門逛街兩三個小時可以用\n\n但是因為XS的電量掉太快\n所以得多帶個行動電源出門\n可是這個包包容納不下\n況且有時候出去玩又要半天以上\n需要背比較多東西\n\n所以\n想買新的斜背包\n使用需求方面：希望至少面料防潑水\n（市面上常見的防水布料材質是CORDURA®、CORDURA\n、X-PAC、PVC）\n以及背起來不會太厚\n預算：一千元上下是沒有問題的\n\n🙏\n不知道各位有什麼推薦的？","excerpt":"事情是這樣的，之前集資買了個h牌的手機包，用了一段時間，覺得不錯用，如果出門逛街兩三個小時可以用，但是因為XS的電量掉太快，所以得多帶個行動電源出門，可是這個包包容納不下，況且有時候出去玩又要半天以上","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"be1a095b-175e-4523-9e06-66a05d939676","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-28T00:44:51.885Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-28T00:55:25.439Z","commentCount":13,"likeCount":20,"tags":[],"topics":["問題","包包","男生穿搭"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"穿搭","forumAlias":"dressup","school":"國立臺北科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":20}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/0e000097-68dd-44df-a7fa-f4e3c76141b7/full.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"4fac8cbc-f572-416a-be26-fc9b98d7f0a1","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/0e000097-68dd-44df-a7fa-f4e3c76141b7/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/0e000097-68dd-44df-a7fa-f4e3c76141b7/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/0e000097-68dd-44df-a7fa-f4e3c76141b7/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-28T00:44:51.885Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-28T00:55:25.439Z","width":640,"height":638},{"id":"4fac8cbc-f572-416a-be26-fc9b98d7f0a1","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/0e000097-68dd-44df-a7fa-f4e3c76141b7/full.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx.dcard.tw/v1